# 能力来源

本 bundle 封装了在被分析仓库中检测到的既有 HTTP 接口。字段名按检测结果原样保留，使 JSON 契约与真实系统一致。

{% for interface in interfaces %}
## {{ interface.slug }} —— `{{ interface.http_method }} {{ interface.route }}`

- 技术栈：{{ interface.stack }}
- 框架：{{ interface.framework }}
- 处理符号：`{{ interface.handler_symbol }}`
{% if interface.handler_path %}
- 源文件：`{{ interface.handler_path }}`
{% endif %}
{% if interface.business_method %}
- 业务方法：`{{ interface.business_method }}`
{% endif %}
- 工具：`tools/{{ interface.module }}.tool.yaml`
- Caller：`scripts/call_{{ interface.module }}.py`
- Endpoint 环境变量：`{{ interface.endpoint_env }}`
- Token 环境变量：`{{ interface.token_env }}`

### 输入模型 —— `{{ interface.request_model }}`

{% if interface.request_fields %}
| 字段 | JSON 类型 | 是否必填 |
|-------|-----------|----------|
{% for field in interface.request_fields %}
| `{{ field.wire }}` | {{ field.schema_type }} | {{ "是" if field.required else "否" }} |
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
无法从源码解析请求负载。在契约确认之前，使用 `--json-body` 传入原始 JSON body。
{% endif %}

### 输出模型 —— `{{ interface.response_model }}`

{% if interface.response_fields %}
| 字段 | JSON 类型 |
|-------|-----------|
{% for field in interface.response_fields %}
| `{{ field.wire }}` | {{ field.schema_type }} |
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
无法从源码解析响应负载。
{% endif %}

{% endfor %}
{%- else -%}
# Capability source

This bundle wraps existing HTTP interfaces detected in the analyzed repository.
Field names are kept exactly as detected so JSON contracts stay faithful to the
live system.

{% for interface in interfaces %}
## {{ interface.slug }} — `{{ interface.http_method }} {{ interface.route }}`

- Stack: {{ interface.stack }}
- Framework: {{ interface.framework }}
- Handler: `{{ interface.handler_symbol }}`
{% if interface.handler_path %}
- Source file: `{{ interface.handler_path }}`
{% endif %}
{% if interface.business_method %}
- Business method: `{{ interface.business_method }}`
{% endif %}
- Tool: `tools/{{ interface.module }}.tool.yaml`
- Caller: `scripts/call_{{ interface.module }}.py`
- Endpoint env: `{{ interface.endpoint_env }}`
- Token env: `{{ interface.token_env }}`

### Input model — `{{ interface.request_model }}`

{% if interface.request_fields %}
| Field | JSON type | Required |
|-------|-----------|----------|
{% for field in interface.request_fields %}
| `{{ field.wire }}` | {{ field.schema_type }} | {{ "yes" if field.required else "no" }} |
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
The request payload could not be resolved from source. Pass a raw JSON body with
`--json-body` until the contract is confirmed.
{% endif %}

### Output model — `{{ interface.response_model }}`

{% if interface.response_fields %}
| Field | JSON type |
|-------|-----------|
{% for field in interface.response_fields %}
| `{{ field.wire }}` | {{ field.schema_type }} |
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
The response payload could not be resolved from source.
{% endif %}

{% endfor %}
{%- endif -%}
